<p>We are looking for volunteers to help us develop this database. Your help is greatly needed and appreciated. We are looking to add pictures of pollen to the system so one can get a picture of what plants the bees are collecting from the environment. This will help users to find out what plants are in the area of the hive. How many. This data is vary useful in planning plantings to provide forage over the course of the year.

